description:
Welcome to the July SWmobile tech talk event hosted at Temple Studios!

This will be our last meetup before we take a short break for the summer and this time we are having a night dedicated to learning more about how apps can be developed with React Native.

Looking forward to see you there!

**Note:** RSVPs will close Monday so we can supply a list of names to venue security. As always if you cannot attend please update your RSVP

**Talks**

* Using Expo to go from zero code to app store submission without XCode or Android Studio - Tom & Charles
* Reactive Native State of Nation - David B

**Timings:**
18:30 Doors open, Food (typically pizza with veg and vegan options) available & drink
19:00 Intro and talks
19:45 Break
20:00 talks
20:45 Finish (tidy up)
21:00 Continue the conversation at near by pub (TBC)

If you are a first time member and/or don't know anyone and would rather pre-meet so you arrive with others please drop us an message via meetup.com (or @scottyab twitter) and we'll arrange it.

If you are keen to speak at a future event please fill in the CFP form[ http://cfp.swmobile.org](http://cfp.swmobile.org)

See you there!
title: July Tech Talk Night - React Native
